|------|-----------|----------------|--------|
| T1 | additem 2001×1 | bag → task 3001 progress → completed → ach 4001 → mail | ✅ Verified |
| T2a | additem 2002×2 | bag → task 3002 progress+1 (only +1, not +2) | ✅ Partial (design) |
